show.description: When humble masseur Veer Jindal is humiliated by his wife Simran and her family, they have no idea he is secretly the billionaire chairman of the powerful Choksi Group. As betrayals unfold and family ties are tested, Veer’s hidden identity shakes their world, exposing greed, loyalty, and the true meaning of love. Watch Now!
